Section 3: Debugging Scenario 1
Command:
docker run nginx

Container stops.

Questions
Why did it stop?
How will you debug?
Which commands will you use?
Solutions :-

1. Root Cause
Container runs in foreground
Terminal exit → container stops

2. Debugging Approach
Check container status
Check logs
Inspect configuration

3. Commands
docker ps -a
docker logs <id>
docker inspect <id>
